des: Returns a list of upcoming group fitness classes at 24 Hour Fitness clubs near you. With hundreds of gyms, thousands of class spaces, and a huge variety of class options from Zumba to Pilates, 24 Hour Fitness has just the right class for you. And now, all of that class information is just one short voice command away. Just say: "Alexa, ask 24GO ...."
